data.name: mission_detail
data.value: Respecting and upholding the rule of law and human rights; By preventing crime, ensuring peace and security and protecting the interests of the government and the people; Providing accessible, efficient, fair and effective justice services that have won public disapproval.
data.comment: Respecting and upholding the rule of law and human rights; By preventing crime, ensuring peace and security and protecting the interests of the government and the people; Providing accessible, efficient, fair and effective justice services that have won public disapproval.

data.name: paragraph_five
data.value: Justice is a reflection of rationality and truth, and by respecting and enforcing the rule of law, I convey my message to you to be the executor and main actor of the change by taking an active part in the work we do to ensure the rule of law and ensure the rule of law.
data.comment: Justice is a reflection of rationality and truth, and by respecting and enforcing the rule of law, I convey my message to you to be the executor and main actor of the change by taking an active part in the work we do to ensure the rule of law and ensure the rule of law.

data.name: paragraph_four
data.value: By ensuring the participation of the public, the institution has become an institution that has gained the trust of the public and the government, which has been started by making the peace of our country safe and sustainable. It is required. Justice is not a matter of choice but a basis of existence.
data.comment: By ensuring the participation of the public, the institution has become an institution that has gained the trust of the public and the government, which has been started by making the peace of our country safe and sustainable. It is required. Justice is not a matter of choice but a basis of existence.

data.name: paragraph_one
data.value: Ministry of Justice: Our country's democracy and justice, rapid and continuous development, and the people's greater benefit cannot be ensured without the rule of law and the practical activities of the justice sector. It will be remembered that the history of our country's justice sector has been plagued by deep-rooted problems of law and procedure as well as attitudes and was a captive of bullies.
data.comment: Ministry of Justice: Our country's democracy and justice, rapid and continuous development, and the people's greater benefit cannot be ensured without the rule of law and the practical activities of the justice sector. It will be remembered that the history of our country's justice sector has been plagued by deep-rooted problems of law and procedure as well as attitudes and was a captive of bullies.

data.name: paragraph_three
data.value: The Ministry of Justice is carrying out its national mission at a higher level than ever before by creating a favorable environment for wide and universal cooperation to bring about the national journey of change, respecting and enforcing the judicial and constitutional system, ensuring the rule of law, ensuring justice, and ensuring the human and democratic rights of citizens. .
data.comment: The Ministry of Justice is carrying out its national mission at a higher level than ever before by creating a favorable environment for wide and universal cooperation to bring about the national journey of change, respecting and enforcing the judicial and constitutional system, ensuring the rule of law, ensuring justice, and ensuring the human and democratic rights of citizens. .

data.name: paragraph_two
data.value: In the new phase of change that has started, our institution has carried out, and is still carrying out, many basic reform activities by carrying out law and justice reform and improving operational problems, by adjusting the treatment of legal prisoners in terms of human rights, ensuring efficient, fair and effective access to justice in institutional services.
data.comment: In the new phase of change that has started, our institution has carried out, and is still carrying out, many basic reform activities by carrying out law and justice reform and improving operational problems, by adjusting the treatment of legal prisoners in terms of human rights, ensuring efficient, fair and effective access to justice in institutional services.
